WHAT THIS LICENSE COVERS

The first-party s2script source in this repository: core/, shim/src/,
shim/include/, games/, packages/, plugins/, examples/, gamedata/, scripts/,
docs/, and website/.


WHAT THIS LICENSE DOES NOT COVER

  * third_party/ — vendored and submoduled dependencies, each under its own
    license (Metamod:Source, Google Breakpad, HDE/MinHook, hl2sdk).

  * The Valve Source 2 SDK (third_party/hl2sdk). Valve's SDK is NOT open
    source and is NOT redistributed under the terms above. s2script compiles
    a small number of Valve SDK translation units into its shipped binaries.
    See licenses/README.md § "The Valve carve-out".

  * Everything statically linked into the shipped binaries — V8, Breakpad,
    protobuf, SQLite, and the Rust crate graph. Their required notices are
    reproduced in licenses/licenses.txt, which ships with every release.

A map of all of the above is in licenses/README.md.
